                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5210" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0824</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8209 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">沈荡黄酒如何定位</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How to develop a positioning strategy for Shendang rice wine?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">戚译，汪曙青</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海盐沈荡酿造有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">传统酿造；大罐发酵；市场细分；目标市场选择；市场定位</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">traditional brewing; big pot fermentation; segmentation; targeting; positioning</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">沈荡酒厂是一家以传统方式酿造黄酒的百年企业，正面临着越来越大的销售压力和营销挑战。作为地方性的小企业，一方面，沈荡品牌的影响力远远不及黄酒行业中的一、二线品牌；另一方面，由于大厂基本上都采用了大罐发酵技术，规模经济使黄酒生产成本大大降低，而沈荡酒厂的高成本传统酿造，使自身在定价和促销上缺乏竞争优势。案例从王总对销售的焦虑到希望寻求专家的建议为引子把读者带到了一个特定的场景――齐教授团队的参访与座谈。通过情节闪回，介绍了沈荡酒厂的前世今生和王总的价值取向；通过现场的人员对话，传达了黄酒行业和沈荡酒厂的基本状况。要使公司走出困境首先需要对沈荡黄酒的品牌进行定位，那么，沈荡酒厂应制定怎样的定位战略？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a century-old company that brews rice wine in a traditional way, Shendang winery is facing increasing sales pressure and marketing challenges. As a local small enterprise, on the one hand，the brand of Shendang is far less influential than the first and second tier rice wine brands, and on the other hand, Shendang winery has no advantage in pricing and sale promotion due to the high cost of traditional brewing process, in contrast to large companies adopting big pot fermentation technology which can reduce the production cost in a large scale. In this case, Manager Wang&#39;s anxiety about sales and seeking for experts’ advice takes readers to a specific scene - the discussion with Professor Qi&#39;s team. The flashback of plot provides the introduction of Shendang winery as well as Manager Wang’s value orientation. The on-site conversation draws the outline of the basic situation of ricewine industry and Shendang winery. The positioning of Shendang brand is essential in order to get Shendang winery out of predicament. Then how to develop a  positioning strategy for Shendang winery?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《营销管理》\《品牌管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销管理 品牌管理 市场定位 品牌定位</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-02</td>
                            </tr>
